{"tid":1418803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[分析文]《從梁天琦思想應用今日既局勢》","createTime":"2019-08-05T20:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T21:31:15.000Z","uid":269622,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22c96b40c34c419a5d4a0a8dbc72d8cdb01faab2","tid":1418803,"uid":269622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:34:35.000Z","msg":"現況.<br />\n8月5日依一杖<br />\n其實見到政府同黑警經已<span style=\"color: red;\">束手無策</span><br />\n只有錄音機式重複說詞<br />\n黑警做到亦都係升級裝備同數量<br />\n但好明顯示威者完全冇因此退後過<br />\n反而不繼升級同還擊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要留意係佢地「分化」招式唔係無效<br />\n只係需要時間</span><br />\n現左每星期示威堵路又慢慢回復之前佔領一樣，不斷重複，再落去同冇新一波行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外，中央已經開啟維穩機器</span><br />\n藍衣人白衣人仲有一班特務/公安<br />\n做既只會就同一招，就係打壓<br />\n不斷將暴力升級，同製造白色恐怖<br />\n今日出棍，明日出刀<br />\n今日出100人，明日出1000人<br />\n今日判幾年，明日判十幾廿年<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但同一樣，又係需要時間制造</span><br />\n所以主導權依然在示威者<br />\n而我地正正就有網絡既<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唯快不破</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n大家要記住<br />\n梁天琦講過我地要做既係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">奪權</span></span><br />\n有權力就可以達到訴求<br />\n奪既，係香港既自主權<br />\n而牌面上「香港政府」有「高度自治」<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">所以我地既目標係擁有所謂權力既「香港政府」亦即是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「林鄭」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n今日可見<br />\nTg放題/圍警署已遍地開花<br />\n黑警疲於奔命，受盡屈辱<br />\n要衰到要交俾鄉黑維持治安<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實黑警關卡已經unlocked<br />\nKO左卒仔，就應該輪到將軍</span></span><br />\n要做既就係升level到各行政機關+「林鄭」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">梁天琦提大家唔好俾仇恨充分頭腦</span></span><br />\n其實就係記住玩狗/趕走黑社會係治療<br />\n並唔係我地要既野！<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n梁天琦亦講過<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府係通過民意授權而組成既機構</span></span><br />\n其實民心所向而加非常清晰<br />\n有足夠民意授權<br />\n各位都唔可以停不斷出招<br />\n示威者只要繼續重奪話語權 （cctvb/記者會)<br />\n分化就唔會成功！<br />\n五年前有人屌過大家<span style=\"color: blue;\">勝利球迷</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">但今次我地要繼續利用依個人性<br />\n保持依個優質同勝利資態<br />\n香港人們一齊贏落去！</span><br />\n<br />\n總結:<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">守</span></span> - 繼續頂住黑警/維穩機器進攻，可由文宣組/當區街坊/和理優/泛民/各界別負責。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攻</span></span>-  勇武既各位，亦都係最珍貴既各位，好應該齊齊level up。方向有二：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">1. 模仿政府</span></span><br />\n就係加大力度模彷一個政府會做既野<br />\n例如做緊既有 臨時立法會(消失左？)，自衛隊，明天既記者會，新聞處 (Freedom Hong Kong)，社會支援系統 (telegram group)，行政會議 (連登) 等等。 網上世界同現實世界其實現在行緊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">雙社會狀態</span></span><br />\n將<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">網上世界已建立既empire，降落在地，就會係目標！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">2. 對準政權</span></span><br />\n今次將會係堅。對準政權🙂<br />\n林鄭同整個管治班子都<span style=\"color: blue;\">毫無認受性，並非由民主選舉産生，係必須下台</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「高度自治」： 香港人治係絕對正確</span></span><br />\n說話唔多講，行動大家自由發揮🙂<br />\n<br />\n原諒我P牌仔分析，覺得講得岩既就推！謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n祝各路英雄，節節勝利。<br />\n並且<br />\n祝願資訊科技發達speed up生活曬所有野<br />\n希望成功既一刻也更快到來<br />\n至撚黑暗既時期未出現已收皮<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"ea319e0f69ad1b359e54ff87a96afc0c03226990","tid":1418803,"uid":269622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:39:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b183932c33c02959bbc2417e9443292d3e308050","tid":1418803,"uid":269622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:39:14.000Z","msg":"幫推唔該"},{"pid":"09aeb2b8f45a61479c6b48b23c66fb652d34f73e","tid":1418803,"uid":217103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:41:28.000Z","msg":"辛苦大家喇！但我想提返你哋一樣嘢！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418774</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家記得返 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時代革命</span>意思<br />\n點解用時代而唔係世代<br />\n係因為呢個係一整個時代嘅抗爭 <br />\n包咗唔同generation 唔同嘅階層<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港時代革命！</span>"},{"pid":"d47ca656197fd54e59af714170a3c23a42fa9e77","tid":1418803,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:53:11.000Z","msg":"有深度文"},{"pid":"1c24ad463ac077e1a7c0549791f5aa3f96624c82","tid":1418803,"uid":269622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:04:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9532a108d462326650bb1ff180b6b96204f985db","tid":1418803,"uid":269622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:06:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21c535142f90fda5ec6e12a61e77b280881388a7","tid":1418803,"uid":134141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:06:21.000Z","msg":"香港人民智未開發到咁先進<br />\n你講既野既重要性或者如何實行<br />\n佢地未必理解到<br />\n理解到都未必願意做<br />\n<br />\n希望手足除左打遊擊同佔路<br />\n可以思考下樓主既方案"},{"pid":"f654a554570ed8b9eb7b9fd6b5a6bf7173bbdbe6","tid":1418803,"uid":138446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:07:44.000Z","msg":"&lt;全部人同我入黎&gt; 下一步 廢除公安條例<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418362</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f5f129b15a71c6c11b5488bada0b333e25ab8df4","tid":1418803,"uid":64003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:09:59.000Z","msg":"各位手足 係時候要搓吓你個心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418847</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"759895b8e64587dc517de7c9afe4963326a5630d","tid":1418803,"uid":269622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:24:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=ed43c211\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA</a>"},{"pid":"c5d2edfe77a6fc5a16fb01cbe8aac45f49079839","tid":1418803,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:31:15.000Z","msg":"推"}]}